  <brief_title>Effect of Cervical Collar in Cervical Radicular Pain.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Conservative Treatment With Cervical Collar in Patients With Cervical Radiculopathy and Radicular Pain. A Randomized Controlled Study</official_title>
